OL,5, An investigation has been launched into
OL,6, 'organised abuse' at a special school  
OL,7, in London after CCTV was discovered of 
OL,8, pupils being physically assaulted and  
OL,9, neglected, BBC News has learned.       
OL,11,FThe videos, found by staff, show pupils
OL,12,Fbeing mistreated in padded seclusion   
OL,13,Frooms between 2014 and 2017.           
OL,15,FOne parent said he didn't know the     
OL,16,Frooms existed until he collected his   
OL,17,F"distressed" autistic son from one.    
OL,19,FThe school says it is working with the 
OL,20,Fpolice and supporting families.        
